{"tid":864684,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"想同今朝地鐵畀我用「巨龍」頂實嘅OL講聲Sorry","createTime":"2018-10-16T11:22:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-23T08:50:56.000Z","uid":14055,"like":34,"dislike":323,"uniUserReply":53,"replies":[{"pid":"85a1bf087051294c1be47a59a8ce26dbb96110d8","tid":864684,"uid":14055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T11:22:37.000Z","msg":"唔洗望，係妳呀<br />\n藍色間條連身裙，細細粒<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今朝葵興等咗好耐先入閘，入到去又等多十幾分鐘，我排妳後面，冇咩特別留意，只係覺得有個斯斯文文嘅女仔排我前面，旁邊啲麻甩佬成日借啲椅偷望咁&hellip;"},{"pid":"b9b520707a88c4e6d1d946600faf187e9f6debe2","tid":864684,"uid":14055,"like":3,"dislike":60,"score":-57,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T11:25:48.000Z","msg":"我同妳一樣，就算等咗勁耐都仲係好平心靜氣，我覺得我地都係高eq嘅一類人，等到九點幾終於有班車到，裡面已經企到開口位，心諗：要等多班又可能要半粒鐘，點都要把握機會&hellip;"},{"pid":"0dca5f4c05067ecf38883dec3bd7c417b600192c","tid":864684,"uid":14055,"like":5,"dislike":37,"score":-32,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T11:29:12.000Z","msg":"一開門，車入面個個好似打欖球咁唔唔畀人出，外面嘅人又冇位入，我見前面嘅妳仲好溫文咁等人出，我靠近妳耳邊輕輕講咗聲：「入啦」，妳先回過神打算要迫入去&hellip;"},{"pid":"b5a7e1fbe94653bb68d8c148af41198d6dae0a28","tid":864684,"uid":22675,"like":3,"dislike":58,"score":-55,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T11:29:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://bbs.a9vg.com/thread-4144431-3-1.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbbs.a9vg.com%2Fthread-4144431-3-1.html&d=s6l9MFVJgpHrcry9F5uOIAhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=1076d57d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bbs.a9vg.com/thread-4144431-3-1.html</a>"},{"pid":"cedd56125e30346eaf5207dd8f35afc28f09d9c3","tid":864684,"uid":69416,"like":131,"dislike":1,"score":130,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T11:34:19.000Z","msg":"警已報<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11a5348260de3a84a3bc81eb392391dcb4a3c3c0","tid":864684,"uid":49974,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"b5a7e1fbe94653bb68d8c148af41198d6dae0a28","tid":864684,"uid":22675,"like":3,"dislike":58,"score":-55,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T11:29:46.000Z","msg":"<a h